name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,es,et,fa,fi,f: Anime Girls Wallpapers and New Tab

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,es,et,fa,fi,f: Anime Girls wallpapers bring your chrome a new look and useful tools
short.en,en_AU,en_GB,en_US,es_419,gu,kn,mr,te: Anime Girls wallpaper turn new tab to custom HD Anime Girls background.

long.ar:
Anime Girls wallpapers bring your chrome a new look and useful tools
Extension Features:

1. Shuffle Anime Girls wallpaper every time you open a new tab. 
2. Randomize Anime Girls  background or favorite it in wallpaper selection panel.
3. Get easy access to popular sites with Google search.
4. Quickly access fun html5 games with the popular games button.
5. Show current date and time automatically.
6. New Note for you to write down your tasks.  
7. Easy access to your history websites. 
8. Easy access to your bookmarks.
9. Add website to Shortcut panel for quick access.
10. Quick access to Google apps.
11. Quick access to More Themes.
12. Easy Sharing to Social Media.
13. Enable fun snow, rain, falling leaves, fireworks animation in Anime Girls new tab.
14. Quick access to your emails and social media accounts.
